<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM1.2.9">
<l>ōti yāyira nāmaṅka ḷuṇarntavark kuṟutuya raṭaiyāmal</l>
<l>ēta miṉṟiniṉ ṟaruḷunam peruntakai yiruntanal limayattu </l>
<l>tātu malkiya piṇṭiviṇ ṭalarkiṉṟataḻaṟpurai yeḻiṉṉōkki</l>
<l>pētai vaṇṭuka ḷeriyeṉa veruvaru piriticeṉ ṟaṭaineñcē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>In the fair Himalayas where our [lord of] great propriety resides,</l>
<l rend="indent">who grants to those who comprehend [him],</l>
<l>Reciting [his] one-thousand names, always being without distress,</l>
<l rend="indent">without suffered sorrows reaching [them],</l>
<l>[My] heart, go and take refuge at Piriti where the simple bees</l>
<l rend="indent">are fearful as they think, ‘Fire!’</l>
<l>Seeing the blaze-like color which blossoms, bursting</l>
<l rend="indent">from the ‘no-sorrow’  tree where pollen abounds.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
